and that users actually

00:09:30.400 --> 00:09:31.735
notice what has changed.

00:09:34.290 --> 00:09:36.990
To make sure that you
land the future release,

00:09:36.990 --> 00:09:39.630
just follow a very
simple process.

00:09:39.630 --> 00:09:42.810
First, ensure that the new
build is technically stable.

00:09:42.810 --> 00:09:45.000
That is just very important.

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.950
It was mentioned in
other talks before,

00:09:46.950 --> 00:09:51.420
but we see that 50% of
one-star reviews on Google Play

00:09:51.420 --> 00:09:55.500
