to engage and retain, right?

00:10:09.420 --> 00:10:12.060
Secondly, leverage
the features you

00:10:12.060 --> 00:10:15.130
have on the Play console,
such as alpha and beta groups,

00:10:15.130 --> 00:10:19.740
go to soft launch, and then
gradually go to full rollout.

00:10:19.740 --> 00:10:23.130
And then for the user,
make sure that you actually

00:10:23.130 --> 00:10:25.860
visually guide them to
what's new in the app,

