doesn't feel like onboarding.

00:12:02.740 --> 00:12:06.940
Ideally it feels like it's
a contextual, core part

00:12:06.940 --> 00:12:10.190
of the user experience.

00:12:10.190 --> 00:12:12.770
A good example, and you see I
